{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"sector4-title","type":"text","text":"# Sector 4: Memory System\n\n**Hybrid Memory: Vector + FTS5 Optimization**\n\nCombining semantic search with keyword search for optimal retrieval","x":50,"y":50,"width":600,"height":100,"color":"#4a90e2"},
		{"id":"memory-architecture","type":"text","text":"```mermaid\ngraph TB\n    subgraph Memory System\n        Query[User Query] --> Detection{Small-Talk\nDetection}\n        \n        Detection -->|Yes| Bypass[Memory Bypass\nDirect LLM Response]\n        \n        Detection -->|No| DualSearch[Dual Search]\n        \n        DualSearch --> Vector[Vector Search\n(Qdrant/ChromaDB)\nSemantic Similarity]\n        DualSearch --> Keyword[FTS5 Keyword Search\nSQLite Full-Text\nExact Matches]\n        \n        Vector --> Merge[Result Merge & Rank]\n        Keyword --> Merge\n        \n        Merge --> ContextGuard[Context Guard\nToken Budget < 2000]\n        \n        ContextGuard -->|Within Budget| LLMContext[LLM Context\nEnhanced with\nRetrieved Memories]\n        \n        ContextGuard -->|Exceeds Budget| Prune[Prune & Trim\nLog Warning]\n        \n        Prune --> LLMContext\n        \n        style Query fill:#4a90e2\n        style Detection fill:#5ba3f5\n        style Bypass fill:#6cb5f8\n        style DualSearch fill:#7dc7fb\n        style Vector fill:#8ed9fe\n        style Keyword fill:#8ed9fe\n        style Merge fill:#9febff\n        style ContextGuard fill:#b0fdff\n        style LLMContext fill:#c1ffff\n    end\n```\n\n**Hybrid Memory System Flow**","x":50,"y":180,"width":800,"height":550,"color":"#e8f4fd"},
		{"id":"vector-search-details","type":"text","text":"## Vector Search Details\n\n**Technology:** Qdrant or ChromaDB\n\n**Process:**\n1. Query → Embedding (OpenAI/Groq embeddings)\n2. Vector comparison (cosine similarity)\n3. Ranked by semantic similarity\n4. Returns conceptually related memories\n\n**Advantages:**\n- Finds related concepts (not just keywords)\n- Tolerates phrasing variations\n- Understands synonyms\n- Handles typos/fuzzy matching\n\n**Use Cases:**\n- \"What tasks did I create yesterday?\"\n- \"How did we implement X feature?\"\n- \"What conversations about Y?\"\n\n**Related:** [[Vector Search]] | [[HybridMemoryManager]]","x":900,"y":180,"width":350,"height":250,"color":"#e8f5e9"},
		{"id":"keyword-search-details","type":"text","text":"## FTS5 Keyword Search\n\n**Technology:** SQLite FTS5 (Full-Text Search v5)\n\n**Process:**\n1. Query → Term parsing\n2. FTS5 index lookup\n3. Relevance ranking\n4. Exact keyword matches\n\n**Advantages:**\n- Fast (native SQLite)\n- Exact keyword matching\n- Prefix matching\n- Stemming support\n- Boolean operators (AND, OR, NOT)\n\n**Use Cases:**\n- \"Show me notes containing 'authentication'\"\n- \"Find mentions of API keys\"\n- \"Search for 'error handling'\"\n\n**Related:** [[FTS5 Keyword Search]] | [[HybridMemoryManager]]","x":1300,"y":180,"width":350,"height":250,"color":"#fff3e0"},
		{"id":"optimization-strategies","type":"text","text":"## Optimization Strategies\n\n### Small-Talk Bypass\n**Reference:** [[Small-Talk Bypass]]\n\n**Detection Patterns:**\n- \"hi\", \"hello\", \"hey\"\n- \"thanks\", \"bye\", \"good morning\"\n- Single words, no question marks\n- Pattern matching on content length\n\n**Benefits:**\n- Saves ~3.8s latency on first token\n- No unnecessary DB calls\n- No embedding generation\n- Reduces planner noise\n\n**Impact:** ~40% of user messages bypass memory\n\n### ContextGuard (Phase 6)\n**Reference:** [[Memory Context Guard]]\n\n**Token Budget Evolution:**\n- Phase 1-5: 12000 tokens\n- Phase 6: < 2000 tokens\n- Improvement: 83% reduction\n\n**Enforcement:**\n- Calculates token count\n- Prunes if exceeds limit\n- Logs warning when trimming\n- Ensures clean LLM context\n\n**Related:** [[Context Gating and Tool Safety]]","x":900,"y":460,"width":750,"height":250,"color":"#e3f2fd"},
		{"id":"known-issues-memory","type":"text","text":"## Known Issues\n\n### 🔴 Critical: FTS5 Running for Trivial Messages\n**Reference:** [[FTS5 Memory Search Running Unnecessarily]]\n\n**Symptoms:**\n- \"hi\", \"hhhii\" trigger memory search\n- Unnecessary DB calls\n- Unnecessary embeddings\n- Planner noise\n\n**Root Cause:**\n- Small-talk detection not comprehensive\n- Memory runs before intent classification\n\n**Status:** 🟡 IMPORTANT - Investigation ongoing\n\n### 🟡 Important: Context Token Bloat\n**Reference:** [[Context Builder Token Bloat]]\n\n**Measurements:**\n- 2424 tokens (before Phase 6)\n- 3.8s first token latency\n- Target: < 2000 tokens\n- Current: ~2100 (still high)\n\n**Progress:**\n- Removed inline context fallback\n- Added ContextGuard enforcement\n- Still needs refinement\n\n**Status:** 🟡 Refinement ongoing\n\n### Impact Assessment\n| Issue | Impact | Priority | Fix Complexity |\n|-------|--------|----------|----------------|\n| FTS5 Trivial Search | Medium | P1 | Low |\n| Context Bloat | High | P1 | Medium |","x":50,"y":770,"width":800,"height":320,"color":"#ffebee"},
		{"id":"performance-metrics","type":"text","text":"## Performance Metrics\n\n### Before Phase 6 (Context Gating)\n- Token count: 2424 tokens\n- First token latency: 3.8s\n- Memory search: Always runs\n- Tool misuse: Frequent\n\n### After Phase 6\n- Token count: ~2100 tokens (⬇️ 300)\n- First token latency: 2.9s (⬇️ 0.9s)\n- Memory search: 40% bypassed\n- Tool misuse: Reduced\n\n### After Phase 7 (Trace + TTS)\n- Trace visibility: Full observability\n- TTS priority: Predictable order\n- Debugging: Much easier\n\n### Phase 8 Goals (MEGA Era)\n- Query interpretation: Advanced\n- Inference: Zero-shot\n- Multimodal: Enhanced\n- Context: Improved retention\n\n### Benchmark Suite\n```bash\n# Run all\npytest tests/ -v --asyncio-mode=auto\n\n# Phase 6-8 specific\npytest tests/test_phase6*.py tests/test_phase7*.py -v\n\n# Performance benchmarks\npython verification/run_benchmarks.py\n```","x":900,"y":770,"width":750,"height":320,"color":"#e8f5e9"}
	],
